    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Data Wrangling\"\nsubtitle: \"Parsing, classificação, mídia e enriquecimento\"\nauthor: \"Marlon L.\"\ndate: today\nformat:\n  html:\n    toc: true\n    toc-depth: 3\n    code-fold: true\n    theme: cosmo\nexecute:\n  warning: false\n  echo: false\n---\n\n\n\n📁 Projeto: whatsapp\\-interaction\\-analysis\n\n# Data Wrangling\n\nCom o arquivo limpo gerado no [Data Cleaning](01-data-cleaning.qmd), esta etapa transforma o TXT em um DataFrame estruturado, vincula arquivos de mídia, integra transcrições e exporta os dados enriquecidos.\n\n## Objetivo\n\n-   ✅ Parsing: TXT → DataFrame\n-   ✅ Classificação: Identificar tipos de mensagem\n-   ✅ Mídia: Vincular arquivos físicos\n-   ✅ Transcrição: Integrar transcrições existentes\n-   ✅ Enriquecimento: Substituir mídias por transcrições\n-   ✅ Exportação: CSV + TXTs de corpus\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n## Configuração do Pipeline\n\n::: {#f15690b3 .cell execution_count=2}\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n</style>\n<table id=\"T_0483a\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_0483a_level0_col0\" class=\"col_heading level0 col0\" >Parâmetro</th>\n      <th id=\"T_0483a_level0_col1\" class=\"col_heading level0 col1\" >Valor</th>\n      <th id=\"T_0483a_level0_col2\" class=\"col_heading level0 col2\" >Path</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row0_col0\" class=\"data row0 col0\" >Entrada</td>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row0_col1\" class=\"data row0 col1\" ><code>raw-data_cln7.txt</code></td>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row0_col2\" class=\"data row0 col2\" >~/whatsapp-interaction-analysis/data/interim/export_2024-10_2025-10</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row1_col0\" class=\"data row1 col0\" >Saída</td>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row1_col1\" class=\"data row1 col1\" ><code>export_2024-10_2025-10</code></td>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row1_col2\" class=\"data row1 col2\" >~/whatsapp-interaction-analysis/data/processed/export_2024-10_2025-10</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row2_col0\" class=\"data row2 col0\" >Mídia</td>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row2_col1\" class=\"data row2 col1\" ><code>media</code></td>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row2_col2\" class=\"data row2 col2\" >~/whatsapp-interaction-analysis/data/raw/export_2024-10_2025-10/media</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row3_col0\" class=\"data row3 col0\" >Transcrições</td>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row3_col1\" class=\"data row3 col1\" ><code>transcriptions.csv</code></td>\n      <td id=\"T_0483a_row3_col2\" class=\"data row3 col2\" >~/whatsapp-interaction-analysis/data/processed/export_2024-10_2025-10</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n## Execução do Pipeline\n\n\n\n::: {#8b1610c6 .cell execution_count=4}\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n</style>\n<table id=\"T_d3460\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_d3460_level0_col0\" class=\"col_heading level0 col0\" >#</th>\n      <th id=\"T_d3460_level0_col1\" class=\"col_heading level0 col1\" >Etapa</th>\n      <th id=\"T_d3460_level0_col2\" class=\"col_heading level0 col2\" >Resultado</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_d3460_row0_col0\" class=\"data row0 col0\" >1</td>\n      <td id=\"T_d3460_row0_col1\" class=\"data row0 col1\" >Parse</td>\n      <td id=\"T_d3460_row0_col2\" class=\"data row0 col2\" >91,924 mensagens</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_d3460_row1_col0\" class=\"data row1 col0\" >2</td>\n      <td id=\"T_d3460_row1_col1\" class=\"data row1 col1\" >Classificação</td>\n      <td id=\"T_d3460_row1_col2\" class=\"data row1 col2\" >21 tipos identificados</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_d3460_row2_col0\" class=\"data row2 col0\" >3</td>\n      <td id=\"T_d3460_row2_col1\" class=\"data r